These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, apricot, ebony, lilac
House: townhouse, modern, cape-cod, tower
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, engineer, entrepreneur, paramedic
1. the entrepreneur is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the paramedic is the townhouse house##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
5. the modern house is between the entrepreneur and the person who likes apricot##2
6. the engineer is the cape-cod house##1
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Color        | ebony | lilac  | apricot | chestnut  |
| House         | tower    | modern  | townhouse       | cape-cod     |
| Job   | entrepreneur     | librarian | paramedic       | engineer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, december, november
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pepper, plum, eggplant
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, 7up, almond-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person eating eggplant and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person eating eggplant is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person eating plum is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Birthday         | august | february    | november  | december |
| Food   | eggplant  | avocado  | pepper   | plum    |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | almond-milk | milk | 7up      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, goldfish, turtle
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, swisher, baccarat
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, yellow, pink, emerald
1. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes emerald and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes black is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
7. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | chinchilla | turtle         | fish   | goldfish    |
| Cigar         | oliveros | baccarat | bluemaster | swisher |
| Color   | pink   | yellow        | emerald      | black   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, daisy, sunflower
House: ranch-style, craftsman, art-deco, colonial
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, fishing, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who growssunflower##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growslily##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the ranch-style house and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Flower   | sunflower        | amaryllis   | lily | daisy |
| House         | art-deco | ranch-style | craftsman    | colonial |
| Hobby     | fishing       | puzzles     | card-games       | rock-climbing    |

