.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, green, grey
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, italian, dutch, chinese
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, january, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes ebony##2
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes grey##1
3. the dutch is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the italian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in january and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Color   | brown | grey      | ebony       | green   |
| Nationality      | colombian   | italian  | chinese | dutch     |
| Birthday      | june     | october | january        | september |

