.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, pall-mall, cain
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, cat, goat
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, doctor, musician
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the doctor##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the analyst##1
4. the musician is on the left of the game-smoker##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the goat and the doctor##2
6. the game-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
7. the analyst is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | game  | fonseca | cain      |
| Pet   | cat  | goat  | rabbit | lizard |
| Job   | musician | analyst | bartender | doctor     |

