.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, colombian, italian
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, october, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the colombian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the dutch is between the person playing bridge and the person playing billiard##2
7. the italian is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Nationality          | colombian  | dutch    | italian | spanish  |
| Game   | billiard | mah-jongg       | bridge        | scrabble    |
| Birthday         | december | january | november  | october |

