.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
House: tower, townhouse, gothic-revival, farmhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, canadian, colombian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, july, january
1. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the italian is between the person who's birthday is in january and the townhouse house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| House         | farmhouse  | townhouse | gothic-revival | tower |
| Nationality   | dutch  | colombian | italian   | canadian         |
| Birthday           | may | july  | june   | january      |

