.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, craftsman, victorian
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, turtle, bird
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, go, scrabble
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the owner of the cat is the ranch-style house##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the owner of the turtle is the cape-cod house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the victorian house##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the cat is between the person playing go and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| House          | victorian  | ranch-style    | craftsman | cape-cod       |
| Pet         | bird | cat | dog  | turtle |
| Game   | go   | scrabble      | backgammon  | canasta     |

