.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, chef, dancer, security-guard
House: farmhouse, palace, townhouse, victorian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, blues, trance, salsa
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the dancer is on the far left##1
3. the chef is between the coach and the palace house##2
4. the fan blues is on the right of the security-guard##1
5. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
6. the fan blues is on the right of the security-guard##1
7. the fan salsa is the victorian house##1
8. the fan classical is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | dancer      | security-guard | chef | coach |
| House         | victorian   | palace  | farmhouse | townhouse |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | classical   | blues | trance |

