.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery, western, musical
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, aconite, dahlia
House: craftsman, palace, ranch-style, farmhouse
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the ranch-style house is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the craftsman house is between the person who growsiris and the person who growsaconite##2
4. the person who growsaconite is between the craftsman house and the person watching musical movies##2
5. the person who growsaconite is the farmhouse house##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is the palace house##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | musical  | western | time-travel | mystery     |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite   | dahlia  | iris    |
| House     | palace        | farmhouse       | craftsman      | ranch-style |

