.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, western, time-travel
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, nurse, fisherman, bartender
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, october, march
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the bartender is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching western movies and the nurse##2
4. the fisherman is on the far left##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western     | comedy | satire       |
| Job      | fisherman  | bartender | firefighter  | nurse |
| Birthday        | march  | december      | october        | august      |

