3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing snooker is the ranch-style house##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the firefighter##1
6. the person playing whist is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
