.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different games are played: billiard, go, backgammon, snooker
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, ferret, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting, parkour, rowing
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing backgammon##2
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game           | go | snooker | backgammon    | billiard   |
| Pet   | ferret      | frog   | snake | goldfish |
| Sport     | snowboarding     | weightlifting       | parkour        | rowing    |

