.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, basketball, climbing
City: marseilles, paris, berlin, hannover
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, palace, cape-cod
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is basketball and the futuristic house##2
3. the person who's sport is basketball is the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person traveling to berlin and the cape-cod house##2
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the gothic-revival house is between the palace house and the person traveling to hannover##2
7. the person traveling to marseilles is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | swimming   | climbing |
| City   | marseilles  | paris    | berlin   | hannover     |
| House   | cape-cod  | palace | gothic-revival | futuristic   |

