.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, aquamarine, mauve, light-blue
House: futuristic, townhouse, victorian, cape-cod
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, daffodil, poppy
1. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
2. the victorian house is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who growsdaffodil##2
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
5. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1
7. the person who likes mauve is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Color   | turquise    | aquamarine | light-blue           | mauve |
| House       | futuristic | victorian    | townhouse          | cape-cod   |
| Flower      | daffodil  | rose   | poppy | balloon-flower  |

