.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, bolivar, game
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, monopoly, go
City: san-francisco, hannover, rome, prague
1. the person playing monopoly is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the game-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to prague is between the dannemann-smoker and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
7. the person playing go is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar      | bolivar | tiparillo | dannemann     | game   |
| Game   | canasta | go        | monopoly  | whist  |
| City           | san-francisco      | prague         | hannover | rome |

