.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, fanta, iced-tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, green, coral, light-blue
There are 4 different nationalities: french, colombian, italian, malaysian
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
5. the malaysian is the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes green is between the person drinking iced-tea and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage        | iced-tea | juice | 7up | fanta |
| Color         | chestnut       | green     | coral   | light-blue   |
| Nationality   | french | colombian | italian | malaysian |

 